<div class="letter-modal" id="letterRiriModal">
  <div class="letter-paper">
    <button class="letter-modal-close" data-close-letter aria-label="Close">✕</button>
    <h4>To my sweet girl,</h4>
    <p>Hi baby! You're probably wondering about what I'm doing right now — nasa laptop ako. I didn't actually finish my letter for you, so I'm trying to catch up right now. You know, baby, it's so hard keeping this surprise from you since ang daldal ko and you know how I am naman.</p>
    <p>I don't actually know what to put in this letter, so I apologize if it comes out a little unorganized. But please know that I mean every word I say to you, and that I genuinely love you.</p>
    <p>Haze ko, I know it's inevitable for us to get hurt and scared while we're in a relationship. But please remember that I would always rather fix us and talk through every problem with you than lose you. I apologize for all my shortcomings and for the ways I've hurt you. Please remember that despite that, I love you with all my heart. I'm willing to go through changes for you, baby. I'll reassure you in every way I can as well. I'll always love you genuinely and wholeheartedly. You're my always, in all ways.</p>
    <p>Consider this letter a good luck message for your exam as well. I know you'll do great, and I'll always be proud of you no matter what. I'm always here rooting for you too. Kampi tayo, diba?</p>
    <p>It's only been a month since I ended the bet, but in that short time, you've made me do things I couldn't even do with others for months. Thank you for always reassuring me and for making me feel loved in every way you can.</p>
